name: Wald
description:
Leander Herzog

Wald, 2021

https://leanderherzog.ch/2021/wald/

This svg path emerges from a random walk with a million iterations. It’s closed and filled black by default, as defined by the svg spec.

Press SPACE or click to run.
F to toggle fullscreen.
S to save an SVG.
A to toggle a 10s interval.

You can print this, at any size and quality you like.
